<subSubSection id="C3696508FFDBFFB63F97F930FD19F896" pageId="4" pageNumber="111" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BCC3683FFDBFFB63F97F930FD19F896" blockId="4.[166,1225,1317,1856]" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">
Diagnosis. Species 
<taxonomicName id="4C734D00FFDBFFB63E9AF930FDAFF929" authorityName="Zerova" authorityYear="1972" box="[470,636,1765,1791]" class="Insecta" family="Eurytomidae" genus="Systole" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="complanata">
<emphasis id="B907EA91FFDBFFB63E9AF930FDAFF929" box="[470,636,1765,1791]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">S. complanata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is differentiated from other 
<taxonomicName id="4C734D00FFDBFFB63C82F930FBA4F8D6" box="[974,1143,1765,1792]" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">
<emphasis id="B907EA91FFDBFFB63C82F930FBCFF929" box="[974,1052,1765,1791]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">Systole</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
by flat dorsum, shorter pronotal collar and slightly elongated stigma. Specimens from 
<collectingCountry id="F3647613FFDBFFB63B1BF8D0FB5AF8F6" box="[1111,1161,1797,1824]" name="Iran" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">Iran</collectingCountry>
were compared with 
<typeStatus id="54C88821FFDBFFB63E13F8F0FE42F896" box="[351,401,1829,1856]" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">type</typeStatus>
material of 
<taxonomicName id="4C734D00FFDBFFB63D52F8F0FD11F8E9" authorityName="Zerova" authorityYear="1972" box="[542,706,1829,1855]" class="Insecta" family="Eurytomidae" genus="Systole" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="111" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="complanata">
<emphasis id="B907EA91FFDBFFB63D52F8F0FD11F8E9" box="[542,706,1829,1855]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="111">S. complanata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
